data.title: Nina – Free Korean Dogs

data.text:
Nina was one of the seven lucky puppies who was born from a mother dog rescued from the Dangjin dog meat farm in Korea last year.

She is a sweet and gentle girl. She is good with other dogs and doesn’t like to fight.

Nina has the most gentle and sweet personality and temperament.

Vaccination Details

DHPPL, Canine Influenza, Kennel Cough, Rabies, Corona, Heartworm test, Giardia test, Flea & tick & heartworm prevention are all done.
